Introducing to you : Visual Stories
Now you can create Visual Stories on the Issuu app straight from your uploaded content. With just a few clicks you can build, preview and share Stories on Instagram and publish in the AMP format to broaden your audience and tap into the power of mobile Stories—today’s hottest content format.
